ribed in combination with antipsychotics or other antidopaminergic agents (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/40360/', '', 'Amisulpride, Lumateperone, Cariprazine, Pimavanserin', 'Dexfenfluramine, Orlistat, Naltrexone', 1767369485);
