cribed in combination with antipsychotics or other antidopaminergic agents (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/40425/', '', 'Valbenazine, Dalfampridine, Sodium oxybate, Riluzole, Inotersen, Pitolisant, Amifampridine, Deutetrabenazine, Tafamidis', 'Dexfenfluramine, Naltrexone, Ephedrine, Phentermine, Orlistat, Diethylpropion, Mazindol', 1767369485);
